Angular CLI:
    -> utility, helps us to generate component,, facilities,, to develop angular app, we use angular CLI

install angular CLI:
        -> `npm install -g @angular/cli`            g-> global

-> `ng new cwh-todo-list`
-> `app.module.ts` entry point file

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Bootstarp:
-> install bootstarp in angular
-> `npm install bootstrap`
-> npm install jquery

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Components
-> `ng g c component_name`

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Directives
-> *ngFor (for loop )
-> custom html attributes

